RocketPack is a GitHub and SemVer based dependency
management system for PHP 5.3 applications running
on *nix using the RocketSled framework.

See also: http://semver.org/

A typical rocketpack.config.php file should looke
like this:

<?php
    //note the second argument here is major, minor, patch
    //versions
    rocketpack\Install::package('YourPackage',array(1,1,1));

    rocketpack\Dependcies::register(function()'
    {
        rocketpack\Dependency::forPackage('Murphy')
        ->add('Args',array(0,1,0))
        ->verify();
    });
